						<div class="postbody">I'd consider clocking it at 113.667 CPU cycles per sample so that it can be used from cycle-timed code.
<br />
<br />And it shouldn't be too hard to support wavetables at any power-of-2 length: just have an AND and an OR between the frequency counter and the address generator.
<br />
<br />Does this mixer have volume control? Does the PIC even have a multiplier?</div>

